## 2. The Thoughts page (`thoughts.html`)
 
This is a list of writing. Each entry looks like this:
 
```html
<li>
  <a href="#">
    <span class="title">A Title for Your First Post</span>
    <span class="leaders"></span>
    <time>2026.05.01</time>
  </a>
</li>
```
 
**Three things you can change per entry:**
- `href="#"` → the link to the post (a URL, or leave `#` for now).
- the text inside `<span class="title"> … </span>` → the title.
- the text inside `<time> … </time>` → the date (use the `YYYY.MM.DD` format so it lines up).
**Leave `<span class="leaders"></span>` exactly as-is** — that's the dotted line, and it fills in automatically.
 
**To add a new post:** copy one whole `<li> … </li>` block (from `<li>` to `</li>`) and paste it directly below, then edit the title, date, and link. Newest posts go at the **top**.
 
**To remove a post:** delete one full `<li> … </li>` block.
 
