## (Advanced, optional) Changing the menu
 
The menu is the same on all three pages. To rename or add a link, edit the
`<nav>` block in **every** file so they match, and put `class="active"` on the
link for the page you're currently on:
 
```html
<li><a class="active" href="index.html">About</a></li>
<li><a href="thoughts.html">Thoughts</a></li>
<li><a href="projects.html">Projects</a></li>
```
 
Most of the time you'll never need to touch this.
